### Instance API Tests
### Tests for InstanceController endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### OpenCode server: http://localhost:4096

### Get all instances
### Returns a list of all server instances
GET http://localhost:8080/api/instances/
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create new instance
### Creates a new server instance
### Note: This endpoint returns 501 (Not Implemented)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/instances/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "new-instance",
  "config": {
    "provider": "zai",
    "model": "glm-4.7"
  }
}

###

### Delete instance
### Deletes a specific server instance
# @prompt instanceId Replace with actual instance ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/instances/{{instanceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

###
